1239
01:30:51,451 --> 01:30:53,286
Thank you.

1240
01:30:59,626 --> 01:31:02,087
Why'd you do that?

1241
01:31:02,170 --> 01:31:04,673
'Cause I knew you wouldn't.

1242
01:31:06,508 --> 01:31:09,803
You said before your parents use you
to get back at each other.

1243
01:31:09,886 --> 01:31:13,348
Wouldn't I be outstanding
in that capacity?

1244
01:31:16,142 --> 01:31:18,978
Were you really disgusted about
what I did with my lipstick?

1245
01:31:19,020 --> 01:31:20,814
Truth?

1246
01:31:22,315 --> 01:31:23,274
Truth.

1247
01:31:24,484 --> 01:31:25,527
No.

1248
01:31:34,911 --> 01:31:36,996
What happened to you?

1249
01:31:38,748 --> 01:31:40,750
Why? Claire did it.

1250
01:31:45,755 --> 01:31:47,507
What's wrong?

1251
01:31:47,549 --> 01:31:50,677
Nothing's wrong. It's just...

1252
01:31:50,760 --> 01:31:52,429
just so different.

1253
01:31:54,347 --> 01:31:56,933
I can see your face.

1254
01:31:57,017 --> 01:31:59,394
Is that good or bad?

1255
01:32:00,770 --> 01:32:02,439
That's good.

1256
01:32:17,287 --> 01:32:18,788
See you, Brian.

1257
01:32:20,790 --> 01:32:22,751
See you next Saturday.

1258
01:32:22,792 --> 01:32:24,294
You bet.

